org.springframework.web.reactive.accept

Class CompositeContentTypeResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.reactive.accept.CompositeContentTypeResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MappingContentTypeResolver, RequestedContentTypeResolver

    public class CompositeContentTypeResolver
extends Object
implements MappingContentTypeResolver
    A RequestedContentTypeResolver that contains and delegates to a list of other resolvers.

    Also an implementation of MappingContentTypeResolver that delegates to those resolvers from the list that are also of type MappingContentTypeResolver.

    Since:
    5.0
    Author:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
